data.description: Recent improvements make this property An excellent choice including new HVAC,new interior paint throughout the home, Gated with A Fabulous View ! Location, Pool & Sun room on smaller lot over looking the lake! New roof & Granite countertops in kitchen with breakfast room. 3 or 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, Extra Large Master suite, Upstairs media room or 4th bedroom and tons of storage.(This is the only upstairs room.)All flooring has been updated.Russellville Schools & School choice is available in our area.This location is only 15 min. from everything ! Looking for an offer !
